    <item>
      <title>add sharing buttons</title>
      <link>http://antweiss.com/blog/add-sharing-buttons/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Mar 2016 13:12:22 +0200</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://antweiss.com/blog/add-sharing-buttons/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;this is becoming my official personal blog and I&amp;rsquo;m inclined to post some quality content here.
so I better add some sharing buttons.
but how does one do this in Hugo?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I recalled I had a &lt;a href=&#34;https://shareaholic.com/&#34;&gt;Shareaholic&lt;/a&gt; account I&amp;rsquo;ve used before. Shareaholic is free and very easy to set up.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve generated the code snippets from their control interface and pasted them to my theme&amp;rsquo;s layout html files (I&amp;rsquo;m using the wonderfully minimal &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/nishanths/cocoa-hugo-theme&#34;&gt;cocoa theme&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;in themes/cocoa/layouts/partials/head.html :
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #ffffff&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;text/javascript&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;//my.shareaholic.url/assets/pub/shareaholic.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;data-shr-siteid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;4c511..e8c&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;data-cfasync&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;false&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;async&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

and in themes/cocoa/layouts/blog/single.html :
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #ffffff&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;br&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;shareaholic-canvas&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;data-app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;share_buttons&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;data-app-id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;somenumberfromshareaholic&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #2838b0&#34;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #388038&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #666666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #b83838&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;disqus&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #888888&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

Voila - the sharing buttons are right here below this post. Sharing makes you richer!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
