      <guid>http://antweiss.com/blog/starting-the-blog/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;ve been reading the posts on &lt;a href=&#34;http://otomato.link/otoblog-2/&#34;&gt;otomato&lt;/a&gt; blog  - you know that until now it was a mixed bag of professional articles, technical tips and personal impressions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now that &lt;a href=&#34;http://otomato.link&#34;&gt;Otomato&lt;/a&gt; is becoming a full-blown consulting firm I feel it&amp;rsquo;s time to separate the personal from the professional.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There still may be some shared context here and there, but starting today I&amp;rsquo;m moving my personal blogging to a Hugo-based site hosted on Github pages (here)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
